getEdgeType

public obvious.data.Graph.EdgeType getEdgeType(obvious.data.Edge edge)
Indicates if the graph is made of directed edges. In Prefuse graph, all edges follow the same "directed" attributes. There is no distinction between edges in a prefuse graph so in this implementation.

Specified by:
